			<h2><a class="title" href="https://otoolefan.wordpress.com/2020/06/16/romance-novel-parody-the-stiffening-kinship-chapter-1-bon-voyage/" rel="bookmark">Romance Novel Parody: The Stiffening Kinship ~ Chapter 1 ~ Bon&nbsp;Voyage</a></h2>
			<div class="info">
				<span class="date">June 16, 2020</span>
				<span class="author"><a href="https://otoolefan.wordpress.com/author/otoolefan/" title="Posts by OTOOLEFAN" rel="author">OTOOLEFAN</a></span>								<span class="comments"><a href="https://otoolefan.wordpress.com/2020/06/16/romance-novel-parody-the-stiffening-kinship-chapter-1-bon-voyage/#comments">1 comment</a></span>
