				<span class="author"><a href="https://otoolefan.wordpress.com/author/otoolefan/" title="Posts by OTOOLEFAN" rel="author">OTOOLEFAN</a></span>								<span class="comments"><a href="https://otoolefan.wordpress.com/2020/05/31/rebel-with-a-cause-the-shocking-story-of-a-young-man-who-gave-humanity-the-finger-chapter-2-short-novel/#comments">1 comment</a></span>
